Repostan because I put some thought into it and am curious to hear what other anons have to say

Body modification on anthros is a whole world of opportunity. There is so many new ways that an anthro can get piercings or dye or other features.
Piercings at the base of the tail, on their larger ears, snout. I'm sure cookie piercings would look interesting if your worldbuilding includes them. Their fur could be dyed in a vast array of ways, basically equivalent to tattoos on humans; patterns, colour gradients, text, flat colour, non-natural colours. You could even do away with the fur too like shaving patterns into it or aesthetic shaving like on poodles. On the more extreme side you can have ear clipping and tail docking.

Just a few ideas to think about. What anthro body mods would you guys be into your waifurs having?
